{"type": "article", "id": 17779, "title": "大理石和黄铜文具", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-19T06:30:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004252ZWkYJbUtNOwPT7yr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t大理石和黄铜似乎是最近的热门搭配，两者之间在材质、颜色上的对比往往能凸显出一种奇妙的张力。墨西哥的设计工作室 peca studio 将这个搭配做成桌上的文具产品。方块的大理石都有小的缺口或起伏，用碗状的黄铜做点缀，一个厚重，一个轻快，成为互补的搭配。可以是一个笔架，也可以是两个书托，镇纸的装饰，放在桌面上显得别具一格。<a href=\"http://www.kichink.com/stores/pecashop?byp455=true#.VkxBmrQV7Vo\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004250qiNVQPldXtWfF29T.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69315403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042506eIbgryD0xTEX9wc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004251VJWBzuZro9GiXePj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004251EoKp9zC5Ix2LNg1M.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}